{"tid":1594821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聯署簽到宜家都未夠十萬個，你地對唔對得住義士！？","createTime":"2019-09-25T17:48:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T10:45:14.000Z","uid":235015,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6e37ab748d899e25f3ec5c2ef0ace324e2aef986","tid":1594821,"uid":235015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T17:48:21.000Z","msg":"香港人，正一垃圾！愧對義士！<br />\n<br />\n呢 d《美國白宮聯署》，10 月 1 日共匪国慶前，都仲未夠人簽滿！點對得住犧牲左嘅義士呀！<br />\n<br />\n連特朗普都出埋聲，促中國恪守中英聯合聲明保障香港自由，香港人仲懶懶閒，當佢無到。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1482398-20190925.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1482398-20190925.htm&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXToleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=a4bb7962\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1482398-20190925.htm&h=e3fc3726\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1482398-20190925.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n快 d  同我喺 10 月 1 日前，簽爆推爆呢 d 《美國白宮聯署》！<br />\n<br />\n【 緊急！以下美國白宮聯署仲未夠 10 萬人聯署！簽完後，記得在 email 裏 click confirm！】<br />\n<br />\n1. 請美國行使《全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法》，制裁侵犯人權的香港官員或知名人士。<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2mIGUn2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2mIGUn2&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXToleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=099d8847\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2mIGUn2</a><br />\n(尚欠 8 萬 2 千人聯署，10 月 10 日截止。)<br />\n<br />\n2. 請求美國派美軍前往香港，拯救正被香港警察濫捕、禁錮、虐打、性侵的香港市民。<br />\n(尚欠 3 萬人聯署，10 月 11 日截止。)<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2kk2ZHW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2kk2ZHW&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXToleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=dc490662\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2kk2ZHW</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 請求美國通過《香港保護法案》，暫停向香港警察出售催淚彈、胡椒噴霧、橡膠子彈和其他防暴物品。<br />\n(尚欠 8 萬 6 千人聯署，10 月 14 日截止。)<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2m39jUJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2m39jUJ&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXToleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=c288c071\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2m39jUJ</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 請將香港警察加入《香港人權及民主法案》的制裁名單。<br />\n(尚欠 9 萬人聯署，10 月 16 日截止。)<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2kyBsT1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2kyBsT1&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXToleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=a9c23897\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2kyBsT1</a><br />\n<br />\n5. 請求美國禁止香港警察移民或入境美國。<br />\n(尚欠 3 萬 1 千人聯署，10 月 18 日截止。)<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2kNkwbN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2kNkwbN&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXToleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=10dc5838\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2kNkwbN</a><br />\n<br />\n6. 請求美國承認香港為美國保護區。<br />\n(尚欠 10 萬人聯署，10 月 20 日截止。)<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2kK8y2q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2kK8y2q&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXToleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=1e269f94\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2kK8y2q</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然唔知有冇用，和理非唔該都做番和理非要做既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c6a70797d462972139f89516c33de2b01bd655","tid":1594821,"uid":258770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T17:51:16.000Z","msg":"我覺得起twitter散播中國威脅論會比聯署有用<br />\n白宮聯署係奧巴馬時代既遺物, 本來已經唔係太高成功率 夠10萬只係保證一個回應<br />\n依家直頭無人睇<br />\n<br />\n逼切需要做既野係令廣大美國人覺得必須要制裁中國<br />\n令到下屆總統大選可以再選一個反共派出黎"},{"pid":"c7d25b55523f9f31207a54272c92aed9bffffff2","tid":1594821,"uid":197716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T17:52:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"509da7db7907bc50de824f857b5327ca172b24d9","tid":1594821,"uid":235015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80c6a70797d462972139f89516c33de2b01bd655","tid":1594821,"uid":258770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T17:51:16.000Z","msg":"我覺得起twitter散播中國威脅論會比聯署有用<br />\n白宮聯署係奧巴馬時代既遺物, 本來已經唔係太高成功率 夠10萬只係保證一個回應<br />\n依家直頭無人睇<br />\n<br />\n逼切需要做既野係令廣大美國人覺得必須要制裁中國<